1996;;Faithful;;American;;Paul Mazursky;;Cher, Ryan O'Neal, Chazz Palminteri;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Faithful_(1996_film);;On her twentieth wedding anniversary, Maggie receives a diamond necklace and a price on her head; both from her husband, Jack. While waiting for the signal, all the way from Connecticut, to do the murder, the hitman starts bonding with Maggie instead. Later, Jack shows up himself, complicating the entire situation.